name: Royal Glam Lipstick
description:
COLOUR, CHIC, ELEGANCE

Long lasting, deep colour of the lips is created thanks to specially selected ingredients contained in the formula of Royal GLAM lipstick.

It leaves a very elegant, satin effect on the lips, in seven shades of colours.

Nourishing and regenerating power of the lipstick is due to aloe which is present in the formula. It moistens and cares for them properly.

name: Royal Glam Lip Gloss
description:
COLOUR, CHIC, ELEGANCE

Comfortable application of the lip gloss is guaranteed by a special, flattened shape of the applicator, which evenly and extremely smoothly distributes the noble colours of the cosmetic on the lips.

The “long lasting” formula of the lip gloss allows you to enjoy the favourite shade and velvet effect longer, even for several hours. The addition of aloe significantly improves the condition of the lips – it softens the skin, regenerates chapped lips and nourishes them. Lips not only gain a beautiful, classy colour, but they are moist and smooth.

name: Royal MAT Skin Camouflage Make –Up
description:
Royal Mat Skin Camouflage Make-Up Mattifying and Covering Foundation with Aloe Vera

Technologically advanced formula of the fluid ensures lasting, matte make-up for many hours.A carefully chosen mix of pigments hides blemishes and skin imperfections while maintaining the natural appearance of the skin, without the “mask effect”. Beneficial effects of aloe; make the skin velvety smooth, well moisturized and regenerated. Contains Vit. C and E and natural UVB filter.

name: "2 Skin" Pocket Rouge
description:
SATIN EFFECT


Ultralight, satin, unusually soft texture ensures comfort of application!

It has multifunctional effects: rejuvenates, brightens the complexion, highlights the cheek bones, optically slims the face. The formula of the rouge, with a touch of mica, allows for a uniform, "muslin" colour. Especially obtained silica provides smoothing of skin imperfections. leaving the cheeks smooth as silk! Available in four irresistible shades of colour!

name: Mask Concealer
description:
Easy to apply, so the complexion looks perfect.

Silky consistency of the concealer allows to apply a thin coat, which perfectly blends with the skin.

Contains light silicones, so it can be spread easily and wears all day.

To achieve permanent camouflage, apply powder after using the concealer.

Comes in 3 natural shades of complexion.

name: Precision Eyeliner
description:
Precision is a sophisticated collection of automatic eyeliners.

Lanolin and vegetable waxes condition the delicate skin of eyelids. Silicone microsponges guarantee comfortable application.

Unique polymers make the stick flexible and guarantee unusual precision and make up lasting. The eyeliner makes creating a perfect contour unusually easy!

name: BIG Black Liquid Eyeliner
description:
This Big Black Liquid Eyeliner is for women who are looking for the effect of intense lines and a visibly highlighted look.

Long-lasting effect is achieved due to a polymer film, which gives the formula appropriate flexibility.

Addition of xanthan gum with unique spatial structure provides uniform distribution of pigment, and thus ensures perfectly covering, clear colour line.

Applicator in the form of a very thin felt pen simplifies precise application and allows you to create flawless make-up along the lash line.

The effect of deep, intense black is thanks to Carbon Black formula visibly highlighting look.

name: Volume GIGANTUS Mascara
description:
VOLUME GIGANTUS EXTREMELY BIG EYELASHES

This product guarantees gigantic volume for women who want maximally thickened eyelashes! Extreme volumizing of eyelashes is the advantage of the new formula of mascara containing special fibres. During application of the mascara, the fibres are arranged on the eyelashes, and thus significantly increase their volume.

Natural waxes and provitamin B5 glaze and smooth the eyelashes, so the colour is deeper and more saturated. Fluffy Brush has been specially designed for thin eyelashes. It is wider and has a larger surface area, providing even better coverage of eyelashes!

Adapted to its consistency, it allows for quick and precise 
application of the mascara! The conical shaped tip of the brush simplifies application in the corners of the eyes. Its curly bristles perfectly "capture" eyelashes, and the shorter bristles of the brush leave a large amount mascara on them, which intensifies the effect of volume.

name: Glam&Sexy Volume Mascara
description:
Volume Black

Deep black, extremely thickening mascara guarantees a sexy look!

Extremely thick brush perfectly reaches every eyelash and separately thickens it! 

Tempt with your eyelashes thick 
to a maximum!

name: Glam&Sexy Lipstick
description:
GLOSS LIPSTICK

The effect of the latest cosmetic hit GLAM&SEXY – gives the effect of full, sensuously glossy lips. The active complex “Maxi Lips” contained in it, supporting the production of collagen and elastin in the skin, visibly enlarges the lips, making them fuller even by 30%!

The structure of the lipstick, enriched with specially chosen esters greatly lightens and softens the skin of the lips. The advanced gel formula covers lips with wet, lustrous , subtle colour giving them intense gloss.

The content of vitamin E has anti-age and moistening effect, vitamin C softens the lips, protecting them from drying up. GLAM&SEXY is a modern combination of durability of a lipstick and delicacy of a lip gloss! It does not stick, it does not dry up the lips. It has a delicate, sweet flavour. Tempts with raspberry scent.

name: Lipstick Classic
description:
Perfect quality combined with sophisticated colour create the ultimate and lasting conditioning lipstick.

The conditioning complex with vitamin F, lanolin and aloe extract nourish delicate skin and make the lips soft, elastic and resistant to chapping.

The light silky consistency allows the lipstick to go smoothly, evenly and long lasting pigments guarantee colour and elegance for hours.

The lipstick collection has been prepared in 51 colours, each season supplemented with the most fashionable colours.

name: Glam Wear Glossy Nail Polish
description:
SUPER COVER SHINY NAIL POLISH

A special plasticiser causes; even application without smudges and patches, perfect adhesion to the nail plate, quick drying of the polish on the nails creating flexible layer - it does not break or chip off

Unique components guarantee; perfect cover after the first application, lasting durability on the nails and resistance to water. The “glossy colour effect” gives perfectly wet look without the use of glazers. It does not contain harmful toluene, formaldehyde or camphor compounds .

A flat and wide brush with special bristle means easier and even application of the nail polish even on wide nails, without smudges or patches.

name: Mirror Effect Nail Polish
description:
The Mirror Effect nail polish is designed to provide an amazing shiny metallic effect. The product comes with a brilliant base nail file to ensure you are given the best results.

Available in 8 fantastic shades.

Nail File instructions:

1. File all nail surfaces with the ORANGE side of the base file.

2. Polish all surfaces with the WHITE side of the base file to give your natural nails a high shine buff, the shinier the better!

3. SHAKE the Mirror Effect bottle well and apply one coat to each nail and proceed with the second coat one nail at a time.

4. Apply a top coat only when the nail polish is completely dry.

If you have acrylic of reconstructed nails, you do not need to use the base file.

name: Hologram Effect Nail Polish
description:
The Hologram Effect nail polish is formulated with the highest quality raw material to capture light and transform it into amazing, ever-changing visual effects of liquid swirls and rainbows.

Easy to apply by using the revolutionary base file (which is included in the price) to polish and prime your natural nails to a high shine to then apply the Hologram effect nail polish. No other base coat is needed.

Available in 16 brilliant shades.

1. File all nail surfaces with the PINK side of the base file.

2. Polish all surfaces with the WHITE side of the base file to give your natural nails a high shine buff, the shinier the better!

3. SHAKE the Hologram Effect bottle well and apply one coat to each nail and proceed with the second coat one nail at a time.

4. Apply a top coat only when the nail polish is completely dry.

Acrylic or Reconstructed nails do not require the use of the base file, you can simply apply directly on reconstructed nails.

name: Caviar Effect Nail Art
description:
The Caviar Effect Nail Art is a fantastic creation of glass beads that will cover your nails to create a three-dimensional visual effect and amazing nail art in a few simple steps. 

Available in 12 gorgeous colour!

Step 1: Apply two coats of Nail polish. Use the Caviar pearls before the second coat dries.

Step 2: Press the pearls against your nail softly to ensure adherence.

Step 3: Use the funnel we provide to collect back in the bottle all of the unused pearls.

Step 4: Wait 15 minutes and apply a normal top coat in order to obtain a longer duration.

Be creative and apply the caviar to different fingers, use different coloured first coats or create new designs by mixing two colours!

name: Neutral Ceramic Effect Nail Polish
description:
Ceramic Effect does not require the application of a nail polish base, you can have perfect nails in less time by exclusively using Layla Ceramic Nail Polish Effect for winning features such as, brightness, shine and drying speed. 

There are 75 gorgeous tones in total to choose from, you can't go wrong!

description: Acetone-free fruit scented nail polish remover, enriched with protective ingredients. Protects nails and cuticles against drying.
